search_term.tooltipText: Search term or keyword used by customers to find a product

search_volume.tooltipText: Estimated total count the keyword(s) is searched monthly on Amazon

sponsored_asins.tooltipText: Total count of ASINs running sponsored ads from using that keyword(s)

competing_products.tooltipText: Total count of product showed in customer searches from using that keyword(s)

competitor_rank_avg.tooltipText: Average rank of all competitor ASINs

ranking_competitors_count.tooltipText: Count of competitor ASINs that ranked for the keyword(s)

title_density.tooltipText: Total count of page 1 products from using that keyword(s) in their title

organic_rank.tooltipText: Organic search position result from using that keyword(s)

sponsored_rank.tooltipText: Sponsored ads position in customer searches

sponsored_rank_avg.tooltipText: Average position detected compared to all products in sponsored results

sponsored_rank_count.tooltipText: Count of queried products with the sponsored ads for the keyword(s)

position_rank.tooltipText: Position of the main ASIN, in a multi ASIN search, in search results

relative_rank.tooltipText: Rank of the main ASIN relative it its competitors. For example, if three (3) competitors are ranked better than the main ASIN the relative rank will be four (4)

count_top_10.tooltipText: Total count of ASIN, in a multi ASIN search, that makes it to the position of ten (10) or lower

count_top_50.tooltipText: Total count of ASIN, in a multi ASIN search, that makes it to the position of fifty (50) or lower
